Interface ImageJPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SciJavaPlugin
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AutoscaleMethod<T>, DataType<T>, MinMaxMethod<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAutoscaleMethod, AbstractMinMaxMethod, ConfidenceIntervalAutoscaleMethod, DataType128BitSignedComplexFloat, DataType12BitUnsignedInteger, DataType16BitSignedInteger, DataType16BitUnsignedInteger, DataType1BitUnsignedInteger, DataType32BitSignedFloat, DataType32BitSignedInteger, DataType32BitUnsignedInteger, DataType64BitSignedComplexFloat, DataType64BitSignedFloat, DataType64BitSignedInteger, DataType8BitSignedInteger, DataType8BitUnsignedInteger, DataTypeVariableBitSignedComplexFloat, DataTypeVariableBitSignedFloat, DataTypeVariableBitSignedInteger, DefaultAutoscaleMethod, DefaultMinMaxMethod

    public interface ImageJPlugin
extends SciJavaPlugin
    Top-level interface for ImageJ plugins.

    Plugins discoverable at runtime must implement this interface (usually a subinterface) and be annotated with @Plugin.

    Author:
    Curtis Rueden
    See Also:
    Plugin, PluginService
